- Username: `nurse1`
- Password: `nurse123`

## Running Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/codecreatewrite/nursedesk
cd nursedesk
pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlite3 python-jose \
    passlib[bcrypt] python-dotenv aiofiles
Create a .env file:
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here
Run:
uvicorn api:app --reload
Visit http://localhost:8000/login
